      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for its next owner. While it remains a dependable driver, the exterior shows clear signs of age, including some fading in the clear coat on the roof and a few noticeable door dings. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, it starts up and runs fine, though it could benefit from a routine tune-up soon. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a reasonable price point.",
