    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed through corners thanks to refreshed suspension geometry and reinforced subframe mounting points\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its mileage, the double-VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring optimal cam timing and torque across the rev range. A visceral, high-revving machine for the purist who values mechanical synchronization over showroom perfection.",
      "price": 34500.0,
